      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior, reflects a standard of care that is rarely encountered. Mechanically absolute and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this offering provides an uncompromising driving experience for the most discerning collector.",
