      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of analog driving dynamics. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver a high-revving, linear power band. The mechanical integrity is superlative, with proactive rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive subframe reinforcement already completed. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The suspension maintains factory-spec geometry with zero bushing deflection, while the exterior finish retains its deep, factory luster. This is a meticulously maintained, turn-key example for the purist who demands mechanical perfection.",
